```py
SELECT
 uniqueID,
 surname,
 firstName 
FROM
 politicians 
WHERE
 firstName = "Myles";
```

```py
SELECT
 uniqueID,
 surname,
 firstName 
FROM
 politicians 
WHERE
 firstName = "Myles" 
 OR firstName = "Ruth";
```

```py
SELECT
 uniqueID,
 surname,
 firstName 
FROM
 politicians 
WHERE
 firstName = "Robert"       LIMIT 5;
```

```py
SELECT
 uniqueID,
 surname,
 firstName 
FROM
 politicians 
WHERE
 firstName = "Robert" 
ORDER BY
 surname DESC;
```

```py
SELECT
 uniqueID,
 surname,
 firstName 
FROM
 politicians 
WHERE
 firstName LIKE "Ma__";
```

```py
SELECT
 uniqueID,
 surname,
 firstName,
 comment
FROM
 politicians 
WHERE
 comment     IS NULL;
```

```py
SELECT
 uniqueID,
 surname,
 firstName
FROM
 politicians 
WHERE
 surname     BETWEEN "X" AND "Z";
```

```py
SELECT
 uniqueID,
 surname,
 firstName,
 birthYear
FROM
 politicians 
WHERE
 birthYear     BETWEEN 1980 AND 1990;
```

```py
UPDATE
 politicians 
SET
 displayName = "John Gilbert Alexander"
WHERE
 uniqueID = "Alexander1951";
```

```py
SELECT
 uniqueID,
 surname,
 firstName,
 birthYear,
 CASE 
 WHEN uniqueID = "Frydenberg1971" THEN "Yes" 
 WHEN surname = "Rudd" THEN "No" 
 ELSE "Unsure" 
 END AS "wasTreasurer" 
FROM
 politicians;
```

```py
SELECT
 COUNT(uniqueID) 
FROM
 politicians 
GROUP BY
 gender;
```

```py
SELECT
 politicians.uniqueID,
 politicians.firstName,
 politicians.surname,
 party.partySimplifiedName 
FROM
 politicians 
LEFT JOIN
 party 
 ON politicians.uniqueID = party.uniqueID;
```
